    "type": "external",
    "summary": "Vrijen Attawar and Gus Passov met for the first time to explore mutual interests and potential collaboration. Vrijen shared background on his company Careerspan, which uses AI-driven coaching to help candidates articulate their value propositions and now serves recruiters and employers with better candidate signal. Gus presented his startup focused on physician compensation transparency and benchmarking, addressing widespread dissatisfaction among doctors with their pay \u2014 a pain point Vrijen validated through firsthand feedback from transplant surgeons at a Stanford Med conference in Vail. The conversation identified overlapping interests in AI applications, recruiting/career tech, and healthcare, with both expressing interest in staying connected and exploring ways to help each other.",
